15.46	Lady_Snowblood_(film)	Lady Snowblood (film)	Lady Snowblood (original Japanese title 修羅雪姫, Shurayukihime) is a 1973 Japanese film directed by Toshiya Fujita and starring Meiko Kaji. It is based on a manga comic called Shurayukihime. It is the story of Yuki, a woman who seeks vengeance upon three people who raped her mother and killed her mother's husband and son.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/0/0c/Lady_Snowblood_%28film%29.jpg/220px-Lady_Snowblood_%28film%29.jpg
